<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I know who buys in Wynnum West and what they are comparing. The typical buyer is a young family or upgrader who has been watching Wynnum and Manly West closely, understands the bayside lifestyle appeal, and has made a deliberate decision that Wynnum West gives them the best combination of space, lifestyle access and price. This buyer is informed, motivated and not easily persuaded by marketing that overpromises. What they respond to is an honest, well-presented property that lets them see exactly what they are getting.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Access to the Wynnum-Manly rail line via Manly or Wynnum stations gives residents a CBD commute option that many buyers in this corridor value highly. The Gateway Motorway provides south and north connections for drivers. Wynnum Esplanade, Wynnum's cafes and waterfront parks are a short drive, and the suburb has access to good primary and secondary school catchments that matter to the family buyer segment. Capalaba Park Shopping Centre serves the southern edge, and Wynnum Central covers everyday retail to the east. Wynnum West is a suburb where the fundamentals are sound and the buyer pool is consistent.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Wynnum West Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Bayside Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Bayside Access</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Young family and upgrader demand</p>
